Afrobeat star Davido has announced he’s about to commence the building project that will leave many stunned. The DMW boss, who revealed he recently acquired a new land on Banana Island, shared a photo and videos via his Insta story of the massive sight on which he’s about to build his dream house which he described as the ‘craziest crib ever.’   Davido sets to develop gift land from dad     Rick Ross arrives Lagos 10 years after for Easter concert     Marriage not ticket to financial freedom – Didi Ekanem   Thanking God for his new land acquisition, Davido wrote: “To God be the glory! Just acquired my New land to build my dream home!!” For the videos which displayed the land mass and persons hailing him, the “Jowo” singer wrote: “I’m boutta build the craziest crib y’all ever seen,” he captioned the video.